EVERY DAY new images are made available in the Collage Art App!

With the Collage Art App you can create amazing works of art! Your creativity is your limit, choose from thousands of images to create your montages and share them with your friends! Create your own art gallery and edit whenever you want!
The Collage Art App is an excellent creator of wallpapers and NFTs! Many professionals use the collage art app to create their work and even make money selling their artwork. So create your own images, wallpapers, NFT today! Our team adds new images (PNG) and stickers every day so you never run out of inspiration!

Choose a background for your images and then add your layers, you can:
- Change the opacity;
- Choose the aspect ratio of the image;
- Invert the image;
- Rotate and resize;
- Change the color;
- Change the order of layers;
- Choose photos from your gallery;
- And much more!

The history of the collage art:
A collage may sometimes include magazine and newspaper clippings, ribbons, paint, bits of colored or handmade papers, portions of other artwork or texts, photographs and other found objects, glued to a piece of paper or canvas. The origins of collage can be traced back hundreds of years, but this technique made a dramatic reappearance in the early 20th century as an art form of novelty. And now in the 21st century it's back, much easier and more fun to create!

What are you waiting for? Make your collage art!

Photo Declutter 2 is the newest tool, able to remove undesired objects from your photos in just few taps! It works with any photo and every time!

REMOVE ANY ELEMENT WITH AI
The app works with any photo since it provides both an automatic and a manual tool.
With it, you will be able to remove:
• People;
• Animals;
• Text and signs;
• Cables, wires, lines and similar;
• Vehicles, cars, bicycles, etc;
• Fences, railings;
• Any elements that spoil your photo;
• Small and big objects;
But, if needed, you can also clone any element, flip it, rotate it and place it wherever you want!

3 POWERFUL TOOLS
The app includes:
• The Replicator which is a clone stamp tool, able to remove any object or to clone it;
• The Auto-Eraser, you draw on the object to remove and the algorithm will do everything by itself, quick and easy!
• A Smooth tool, to smooth out parts of the image.

WELL ESTABLISHED ALGORITHM
Photo Declutter (v1) has been rated 4.4 stars, customers love it. 
Photo Declutter 2 is even better, with more features, improved workflows and works offline!

EASY TO USE WITH IN APP EXAMPLES
During the initial tutorial you can take a look at few video examples that let you better understand how you should use the tools correctly.
